knit: (
  function(inputFile, encoding) { 
    
    pOutputName = "OverallAnalysis_Revised"
    
    pOutputSrc = "P1B" 
    
    pDate = format(Sys.time(), '%Y-%m-%d-%Z_%H_%M')
    
    pFileName <- paste(pOutputName,pOutputSrc, pDate, sep = "-") 

    rmarkdown::render( 
      input       = inputFile, 
      encoding    = encoding, 
      params      = list(sub_title = pSubTitle),
      output_dir = paste(dirname(inputFile), "Output", sep = "/"),      
      output_file =  pFileName)
  })
